text: MAASAI are a Swedish duo from Stockholm, formed in 2010. The duo consists of Dominique Teymouri (vocals) and Zackarias Ekelund (drums). ==Members== * Dominique Teymouri * Zackarias Ekelund ==Discography== ===Singles=== * Memories (2013) * The Healer (2013) * Forgive Me (2014) ===Extended plays=== * Frida Sundemo - Snow, MAASAI Remake (2012) ==References== == External links == *JaJaJa Music Spotlight Interview: MAASAI on 15 July 2014 by Emma Pressley Category:Swedish pop music groups
